# Docs Maintenance

- When changing scripts, verification steps, env vars, routing conventions, or Firestore behavior, update `README.md`.
- When changing repo-specific engineering constraints, update `AGENTS.md` or the relevant `.cursor/rules/*.mdc`.
- If MCP tools are mentioned, phrase the guidance conditionally. Do not assume a specific client/runtime exposes them.
